%N A167854 Number of reduced words of length n in Coxeter group on 44 generators S_i with relations (S_i)^2 = (S_i S_j)^15 = I.
%C A167854 The initial terms coincide with those of A170763, although the two sequences are eventually different.
%C A167854 Computed with Magma using commands similar to those used to compute A154638.
%H A167854 G. C. Greubel, <a href="/A167854/b167854.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..500</a>
